Key Match Events: Marcelino Nunez scored for Chile early in the match
Youssouf Fofana equalized for France soon after
Kolo Muani scored and assisted a goal to help France take control

Randal Kolo Muani returned to the starting lineup after missing the previous match
Post-Match Reflections: Didier Deschamps will likely consider Kolo Muani for the left forward position ahead of Euro 2024
Miscellaneous Highlights: Kylian Mbappe endured a night to forget
